Direct Known Subclasses:
AWStaticSiteGenerator.ExtendedDefaultApplication
public class AWDefaultApplication
extends AWConcreteApplication

This is provided as an application-level subclass of AWConcreteAppliction in lieu of the application's having its own subclass. This is used in those situations where we do not have a standard awf application, but we're using the awf to do string rendering or parsing. (for example, the messaging framework)
